					<p class="fs-5">Ways You Can Help</p>
<p class="fs-7">It’s easier than you think to support veterans who are struggling in your community. <a href="https://satruck.org" target="_blank" title="Visit The Salvation Army donations website to donate goods and more" rel="noopener">Donations, including goods and services,</a> can go a long way in helping those who served our nation. <a href="https://salvationarmyusa.org/usa-central-territory/volunteer" title="Find volunteer opportunities at The Salvation Army for you or your organization">Volunteers are always needed, too. Please reach out to The Salvation Army location nearest you to discover how you can help.</a></p>
